Pakistanantolem soglleant vhodd xar. Loksonkhea: 5,103,000 (1989) . Leari ani molir hoya nhomyanchea modim bhuxirachea tonkar hem xar voslam. Pakistanantolem hem ek mukhel bondor. Doreatole eke fatraullichea tonkacher monor namvachi unch xilla asa .He xillekhatir korachi bondrak bori rakhonn melltta. Monoreache fator ani mukhel bhum-i hancheamodlea kharokchchhantoli gallachi mati apxinch zhotaurovim vhamvon vota,hem bondrachem ek soimik khaxeleponn zaun asa.

Korachi xar sindhu nhoinchea mukhakodden vaivyek asa .Hem xar mubom-i saun 880 kimi ontracher ani dil'li saun 1056 kimi.Ontracher asa suejh margan gem xar londdnosaun fokot 3,725 kimi.Ontracher axil'lea yuropak hem soglleant lagxil'lem bondor langi asa.Tebhair ofgannistan, modhy axia hankaim hem bondor lagim poddtta.Hangachem tapman zun tebhair ofgannistan, modhy axia hankaim hem bondor lagim poddtta.Hangachem tapman zun mhoineant 32 so ani zanevari mhoineant 14 se. Asta. Hanga paus 20 sem'mi. Poddtta.

18 vea xenkddoyapoilim korachi xaracho khoinch ul'lekh mellna. 1725 to, hob nhoinchea tonddakodden khorak vattharant lhanxem bondor axil'lem.Hem bondor matyen bhoril'lean tea vattharant raupi lok kolachikun hanga raunk gele. Thoim bhuxirachea tonkar kil'lo bandun he lok raunk lagle.Kolachikun vattharant atanchem korachi xar asa.Korachi xarache namv “kolachikun” hachevelean poddlam asunk zai. Otthravea xenkddoyachea xeuttak korachi xar talpur hangachea miranche sot'tekhala axil'lem .1843 vorsa brittixamni zoit zoddlem. Hoya kallant sor chalsr nepiorchea yotnamni korachi xarachi khubxi udrogot zali.1865 to omerikent yadvi zhuzam zaunk laglim. Dekhun , thoincho kapus inglonddak mellop kotthinn zalo. Oxa vellar bhartantolo kapus mubom-i ani korachi bondrantlean lonkaxor hanga nireat zaunk laglo. Taka lagun kapus mubom-i ani korachi bondrantlean lonkaxor hanga nireat zaunk laglo. Taka lagun korachi bondrachem mhotv khub vaddlem.1935 to zal'lea kaidoyan sindh prant mubom-i xarasaun vegllo kelo, ten'na korachixarak hoya novea prantachi rajdhani keli. Fuddem 1947 to bhartache fallnnevellar pakistan vegllo dex zatkoch korachi pakistanochi rajdhani zali.

Punn kendr sorkarachi torekovar karealoyam, pordexi vokilati ani fallnnek lagun hozaramni nirvasit lok raupak ayil'lean korachi xarak khubxa sonkxttank tondd dimvchem poddlem. Udka purounn ani bholaikevixinche upai korop bhovo kotthinn zale. Oxa vellar 1960 vorsa raullopinddi xarachea lagsar ek novea nograchi yeuzonn keli ani pokistanochi rajdhani thoim vheli. Tika islamabad hem namv dilem. He ghoddnnuken korachi xarantolo tann unno zalo.Punn xarache mhotv unne zaunk nasle. Kaim sorkari karealoyam korachi xarant uril'li.

Ek ughegik xar mhonn korachi xarachi namna asa.Hanga kapus ,rexom' ani lakor hanche kopdde toyar zatat. Hanga ximitt, nolle, vijechi torekovar upkaronnam ,lokhnni saman, gramofonacheo pletti, vokhdam. Rosainam, foska, katddi saman ,kach, saikoliche bhag adiche karkhane asat, matyechim ani dhatuchim aidonam xendreo, toyar kopdde ,galiche hancho hatveusai hanga boretoren cholta.

Vepar, ughegodhonde ani xikxonn hoya mollancher korachi xarak pakistanant khub mhotv asa.Ddrigchea antororaxttri-i manyotai mellil'lea vimanotollakhatir ani borea bondrakhatir pakistan rajeantolo ayatonireaticho vepar korachi xarantlean zata.Hangchean gomv ,dhany,kapus, katddi, kochchi lokor adi malachi nireat zata ani tikhem ,yontram ,suti kopdde , petrol,kallso , sakor adi malachi ayat zata.

Xikxonnavangodda samskritik nodrenuy korachi xarak mohtv asa. Hoya xarant tontrik xikxonnacheo xalla, madhyomik xalla ani korachi vighapitth asa.

Korachi xarant vidhimonddoll ,sochivaloi ,nyai karealoyam ,mohanogor palika, bonko,vimeacheo kompni ,vimanacheo kompni oxeo zaiteo vepari kompni axil'lean hangachi jinn gojbojil'li asta. Hangchea vostusongrohaloyant purvil'lea ovxexancho mhotvacho santtho asa.1971 to zal'lea bharot ani pakistanachea zhuzant korachi bondrache khub luksann zale.


